  "description": "A long-distance view of a landscape featuring two islands in a body of water under a dramatic, overcast sky. The foreground shows a portion of a coastal city with buildings and greenery, gradually receding into the background. The larger island, appearing more prominent, is covered in lush vegetation and has a peak where a patch of cloud seems to rest. The water surrounding the islands reflects the light, creating a shimmering effect. The sky is filled with dark, billowing clouds, suggesting an impending storm or overcast weather. The lighting is soft and diffused due to the cloud cover, resulting in a muted color palette.",
